        <div class="col-7" style="margin-top:20px; margin-left:20px">
            <h1>Classic Lashes</h1>
            <p>
                Classic eyelash extensions are a simple, beautiful, natural-looking lash style.
                They are applied on a 1:1 ratio, which means one extension is attached to one
                natural lash. This gives you a natural looking lash.
            </p>

            <h3> Price:</h3>
            <p>
                $60 1 hr 30 mins full set <br/>

                $40 1hr 30 mins refill (2-3 weeks with at least 50% lashes)
            </p>
            <a asp-controller="Appointment" asp-action="BookAppointment" asp-route-serviceId="2" class="btn btn-primary" id="services">Book an appointment</a>
        </div>
